name: Desjardins Canadian Universe Bond Index ETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of a broad Canadian bond index. The ETF seeks to replicate the performance of the Solactive Canadian Bond Universe TR Index (the 'Index'). The investment strategy of the ETF is to invest, directly or indirectly, in a portfolio of Canadian fixed income securities that closely matches the Index. The Index is composed of Canadian investment-grade fixed income securities issued in the Canadian market, including government, quasi-government and corporate bonds.
